name: UPSC
description: The Union Public Service Commission (UPSC) conducts the Civil Services Examination (CSE) and other competitive exams to recruit candidates for prestigious government positions like IAS, IPS, IFS, and other central services. The exam includes three stages: Prelims, Mains, and Interview.

blogs.title: UPSC Prelims : Preparation Strategy
blogs.description: Understand the key differences between UPSC Prelims and Mains, their syllabus, exam pattern, and best preparation strategies. Get expert tips to crack the UPSC Civil Services Examination successfully!
